Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 军报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹军与袁军在官渡相持大战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来我成就大业的时机到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:00:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}夫君为何如此高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操率军到了官渡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.03,0:01:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许昌必然空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我率军奇袭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.97,0:01:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是千载难逢的好机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}夫君 此事还需从长计议
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}毕竟曹操不是等闲之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.21,0:01:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}夫人不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这次我定要夺取许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.55,0:01:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}杀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}战车阵 进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}铁骑阵 冲阵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}铁骑给我冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这个废物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}进者生 退者死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给我杀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}进攻 杀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}铁甲军 给我冲出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}步军 给我冲出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 主主主公
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们的阵脚已经乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}依在下之见 我们还是撤军吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 再战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}惧战者死 都给我冲出去 快点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 你看 那曹操的铁骑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经冲破我们的中军大阵了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再不撤就来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 主公 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尔等还在那儿愣着干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还不快快把主公架走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏 主公 快撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 听我的 快撤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 走吧 走吧 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 撤 快撤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:07:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}弟兄们 给我斩杀袁绍 冲啊 杀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍逃了 袁绍败了 斩杀袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他若不死 必然复来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}斩杀袁绍 斩杀袁绍 斩杀袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}斩杀袁绍 斩杀袁绍 斩杀袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是来取我性命的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁公 你对我有恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备今日是来报恩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你如何报答我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请袁公先走 我替你抵杭曹军
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备 你带了多少人马
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不足五千
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我堂堂七十万大军都败了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你区区几千人又有何用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你七十万大军都败了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的天哪 你这个仗是怎么打的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这七十万大军
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是伸直了脖子让曹军砍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那也得砍他几天几夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请袁公快走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}重整旗鼓 再战曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恨死我也 苍天助贼 不助我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再不走就来不及了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操 曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奸恶 奸险 奸贼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他明明知道倘若正面厮杀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绝非我敌 因而使出连环奸计
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:10:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一盏茶的功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他竟然使出三道奸计来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先是虚言求和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再者就是将天子让给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有放出宫女来扰乱我的军心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 是四道奸计
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 那曹操之所以请你喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是要有意拖延战机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分明是想利用那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太阳西射的光线 刺射我军目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是我过失 是我糊涂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此战 错在于我 连累三军哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 主公 切勿过于悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这常言道 胜败乃兵家之常嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}况且我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 在下痛定思痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反倒想起一个人来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想起谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别驾田丰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公啊 战前田丰曾多次奏谏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹贼善战 灭曹未必非战不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}应当随机应变 以静制动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公如果专注于富国强兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那三五年后定当不战而胜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悔当初不听他言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才惨遭失败呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}田丰现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在冀州大牢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他怎么在冀州大牢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公你忘了 是你把他关进大牢的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 你不是要把那田丰的首级
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和那曹操的脑袋摆在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一把火烧了祭旗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快 快 快 快 快 快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快去传命 立即开释田丰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 另外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}派我的车驾把他接到官渡大帐来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要重用他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快去 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 依在下之见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}开释田丰即可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然 未必需要重用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公你有所不知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下刚刚接到冀州守将来报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说主公你在官渡战败一事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传回冀州以后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所有的文臣武将和满城的百姓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无不阵痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唯有那田丰小人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他在狱中居然高声欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}得意忘形 狂妄的吹嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.65,0:14:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下实在是不敢直言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 那田丰在狱中仰天长啸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他说你是庸主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚愎自用 不足与为谋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他的先见之明你不听
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以必然有今天这个大败
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这可恶 可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个贼子竟敢如此的藐视我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}持我佩剑立即前往冀州大牢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}立斩田丰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅 各路败兵已经陆续回营了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}清点过后 仍有近四十万
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们主要损失在于辎重和战车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅 我军虽然首战失利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但兵马仍就是曹军的两倍以上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}足以再战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 我们 定要汲取教训
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大破曹军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传令 三军五日内休整 准备再战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别驾大人 你真是料事如神哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说过 曹操善于用兵 伐曹必败
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我刚刚听到消息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公果然在官渡大败了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我多么希望我言错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可不幸又被我言中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想 过不了几日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公定会重新起用大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不了解我家主公
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家主公是外宽内忌 喜怒无常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果我军大胜曹军
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公欢喜之余
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}定会不计前嫌立刻赦我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可现在主公大败
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他一定是恼羞成怒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我命不久已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀别驾 主公口谕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}田丰亵君悖主 罪无可赦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令其自尽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你能告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是许攸还是郭图挑唆主公的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明白了 牢吏呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}麻烦你给我取笔墨来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要给主公写一封遗书
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这位军士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不想死在这牢中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待会可否允许我在星光下自刎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想最后看一眼天象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敬凭尊意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天意助曹 不助袁哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:20:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恨天 恨天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 此役啊 我军斩首八万余级
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}缴获军械 辎重无数啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍已经退回官渡大营
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}挖沟 筑寨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}龟缩着再也不敢接战了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们折损了多少将士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伤约两万 亡约七千多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 真是大获全胜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是我起兵以来 从未有过的大胜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 将士们都乐疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说照这样打下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}转眼就可以打进冀州了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果敌军突然此时来袭你怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么 袁绍要来袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是说如果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你瞅瞅他们酩酊大醉的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果袁绍此时来袭我们必然大败
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然敌军没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是身为中军主将
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就要设想他们前来偷袭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了 我立刻加强布防
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们虽然大胜袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是敌强我弱的基本态势
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.87,0:21:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍手里还有四五十万人马
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}青州 幽州 并州
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还会继续供给他粮饷兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果袁绍知耻而后勇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}后头的仗就更难打
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有 曹仁哪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们的粮草不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 刚才在庆功宴上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.24,0:22:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说我们还有百日之粮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.68,0:22:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我骗你们的 实际上只有十日之粮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.72,0:22:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么 末将建议丞相班师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.49,0:22:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我军是功成凯旋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.03,0:22:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁军是败而心乱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.20,0:22:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍见我等退兵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必然是额手称庆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.23,0:22:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}断然不敢追杀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我何尝不想退军
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:22:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但此时退军 着实可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只恨荀彧不在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他若在 定能帮我一决进退
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公子 丞相在此信中 问我进退
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.41,0:23:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相在信中言 军中粮草殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.08,0:23:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难以久战
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果袁绍得知我军粮草不济
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会坚守不战
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.05,0:23:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我军早晚要陷入被动之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相还说 现在退军甚为可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等于是主动放弃了大好局面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给袁绍以喘息之机
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.84,0:24:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀先生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.70,0:24:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲在信里面把进退利弊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.74,0:24:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}样样都说到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.94,0:24:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那咱们是应该进呢 还是应该退呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.28,0:24:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公子问得好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.58,0:24:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我问你 丞相是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.19,0:24:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.76,0:24:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那好 我告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.63,0:24:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实丞相早有意退军
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.54,0:24:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只不过他不愿意直说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.77,0:24:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其意是想让我劝他退军
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.78,0:24:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.71,0:24:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他就可以和前方的将军讲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.95,0:24:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军中粮草殆尽 荀彧力劝班师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.85,0:24:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不得以而从之
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.29,0:24:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲真是太聪明了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.40,0:25:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相的聪明 不是天下第一
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.23,0:25:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是天下第二
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.27,0:25:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 那 那这天下第一是谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.01,0:25:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虚位以待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.12,0:25:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲既然希望你劝他退军
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.42,0:25:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你打算怎么劝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.00,0:25:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我非但不劝丞相退军
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.00,0:25:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反而要劝丞相进军
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.61,0:25:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相万万不可撤军
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.08,0:25:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍虽大败
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.61,0:25:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但他仍然拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.85,0:25:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}四州富裕之地 万千田亩
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.32,0:25:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不但能够生长出无尽的粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.75,0:25:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也能生长出无尽的兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.99,0:26:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}时间利袁绍 不利丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.66,0:26:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但战局利丞相 而不利于袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.10,0:26:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相应抓住战机 乘胜再战
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.13,0:26:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下以为 此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.03,0:26:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最可怕的不是粮草殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.17,0:26:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乃是丞相的心病
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.67,0:26:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相初战大捷 反而顾虑重重
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.88,0:26:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欲胜惧败 欲进惧挫
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.99,0:26:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有这等臣子 何愁袁氏不灭
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.23,0:26:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 是否班师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.20,0:26:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敢言班师者 斩
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.60,0:26:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传令三军
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.34,0:26:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}备好兵器军械 准备再战
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.64,0:26:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.41,0:26:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 那粮草怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.71,0:26:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州屯有数万粮草
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.18,0:27:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}立刻派飞骑前往徐州调运粮草
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.18,0:27:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.90,0:27:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军师
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.00,0:27:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下仔细看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.30,0:27:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹军布下三重防卫
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.14,0:27:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一重是护卫营
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.74,0:27:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}驻扎在大营数里之外
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.11,0:27:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分布于东南西北四角
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.88,0:27:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第二重是巡骑
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.85,0:27:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}每隔一个时辰
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.21,0:27:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}便有一校尉带百骑巡防
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.38,0:27:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这第三重才是哨位
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.16,0:27:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军师快看 那边出来一个单骑
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.97,0:27:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这肯定是曹营派出求救的信使
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.24,0:27:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}派快马火速追上 将其射翻
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.48,0:27:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.31,0:28:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有封信 走
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.09,0:28:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军师
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.04,0:29:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然不出我的所料
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.55,0:29:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这一回 曹阿瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.78,0:29:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的死期到了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.82,0:29:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.09,0:29:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冀州 幽州的援兵
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.79,0:29:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天已经陆续到达
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.96,0:29:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}青州的十万粮草
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.76,0:29:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}估计明天也可运到
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.03,0:29:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样算来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.17,0:29:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我军有马军八万
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.27,0:29:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}步军二十五万 水军十万
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.01,0:29:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总计不下四十三万
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.48,0:29:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}另外 粮草足可支应百日
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.28,0:29:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.12,0:29:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我军虽然损失了一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.95,0:29:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但依然是兵广粮多
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.92,0:29:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传令 三军十日内休整
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.63,0:30:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之后 看我如何灭曹
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.30,0:30:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 有一件小事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.84,0:30:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}望主公听了不要动怒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.67,0:30:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.74,0:30:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}邺郡太守密报
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.58,0:30:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}该郡本该拨付五万粮饷的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.75,0:30:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但由于许攸之子监守自盗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.88,0:30:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贪污了三万多
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.75,0:30:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因而耽误了此次粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.96,0:30:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这难道还是小事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.79,0:30:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大敌当前 粮饷性命攸关
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.27,0:30:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许子贪污之事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.10,0:30:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸知不知情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.60,0:30:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其子在牢中招供说
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.41,0:30:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸略知一二
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.84,0:30:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为那三万多粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.74,0:30:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是为其父修府邸的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.62,0:30:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸负我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.69,0:31:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这事暂且先搁下
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.29,0:31:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等战事过后
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.46,0:31:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要严查重办
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.73,0:31:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公贤明
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.60,0:31:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.00,0:31:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 主公 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.40,0:31:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹贼败像已现
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.57,0:31:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们是胜机在望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.58,0:31:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}郭图也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.45,0:31:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操如何败像已现啦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.12,0:31:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回主公
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.66,0:31:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今夜初更时分
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.86,0:31:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下亲率部卒
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.83,0:31:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到那曹军大寨探营
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.63,0:31:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但见他布防严密
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.83,0:31:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然没有一丝懈怠
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.44,0:31:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然如此 败象何来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.87,0:31:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公你别急吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.24,0:31:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}且听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.54,0:31:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当我正欲拨马归营时
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.08,0:31:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忽然看见那曹营
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.98,0:31:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辕门处冲出一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.48,0:32:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}径直奔着徐州方向而去 而且
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.82,0:32:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了 那必定是信使
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.63,0:32:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}信使
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.43,0:32:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敢问郭图大人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.67,0:32:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个信使深夜出营
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.84,0:32:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又有何干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.01,0:32:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.38,0:32:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当下我们正与曹军对垒
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.78,0:32:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们大胜之后却壁垒森严
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.25,0:32:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这天到这般时候
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.02,0:32:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放出单人独骑
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.82,0:32:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其中一定有诈
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.95,0:32:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}于是在下急令快马火速追上
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.55,0:32:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用乱箭将其射翻
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.12,0:32:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后 从他的腰间
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.69,0:32:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}搜出了曹操的军令
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.20,0:32:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 你请看
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.08,0:33:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹操分明是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.51,0:33:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}粮草已尽 兵器缺乏
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.82,0:33:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他已经难以支撑了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.82,0:33:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以这才急令徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.19,0:33:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}发运粮草兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.06,0:33:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以解他的官渡之危
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.13,0:33:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.60,0:33:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下也是看完了军令之后
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.80,0:33:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}方才明白
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.47,0:33:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹操布防严密
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.07,0:33:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有一丝懈怠
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.54,0:33:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}全是做给我们看的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.67,0:33:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹操是欲盖弥彰
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.81,0:33:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.21,0:33:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹孟德此刻最害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.25,0:33:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是我们对他的攻袭
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.18,0:33:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸 你有何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.72,0:33:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.29,0:33:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}您应该抓住这个绝好的战机
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.76,0:33:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}四十万大军倾翼而出
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.19,0:33:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兵分两路
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.36,0:33:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一路
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.20,0:33:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以十万人马
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.33,0:33:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}佯攻他在官渡的前敌大营
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.57,0:33:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}另一路
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.60,0:33:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}集三十万精锐
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.53,0:34:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连夜奔袭他的老巢许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.97,0:34:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 我们的这两路人马
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.64,0:34:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无论哪一路能够成功
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.84,0:34:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹贼必败亡
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.91,0:34:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而我许攸几乎可以断言
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.08,0:34:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们的这两路人马都会成功
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.02,0:34:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这 必是曹贼的奸计
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.76,0:34:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岂能瞒得过主公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.23,0:34:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}郭图
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.00,0:34:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么能说这是奸计呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.87,0:34:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹操分明是形同磊卵了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.67,0:34:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操故意在你的眼皮下
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.47,0:34:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放出一个信使
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.04,0:34:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好让你劫得军令
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.78,0:34:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诱骗我军去夜袭曹营
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.61,0:34:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而曹操呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.88,0:34:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早就在那里张网设伏
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.72,0:34:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等着我们去送死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.99,0:34:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.35,0:34:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹贼分明是粮草已尽
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.96,0:34:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兵器缺乏
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.69,0:34:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这可是我们剿灭他
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.19,0:34:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最好的战机啦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.76,0:35:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公如果是让那曹操得到补充
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.93,0:35:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无疑是坐失良机 甚或是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.87,0:35:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.47,0:35:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这道军令万万不可相信
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.77,0:35:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公难道忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.27,0:35:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就在几日前
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.51,0:35:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操还拿天子作为诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.74,0:35:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诈言乞和
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.44,0:35:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连堂堂天子
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.21,0:35:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都能被曹操用来做诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.08,0:35:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何况一道军令呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.29,0:35:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.66,0:35:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我又险些中了曹贼的奸计啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.99,0:35:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.73,0:35:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今后再要献策 定要三思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.71,0:35:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.74,0:35:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操这道军令是否是诡计
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.75,0:35:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们可以暂且不论
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.08,0:35:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但令在下着实没有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.69,0:36:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹操给人诡计多端的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.59,0:36:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}居然比他本人的诡计
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.66,0:36:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还要可怕呀
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.76,0:36:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此话何意
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.63,0:36:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为在你郭图眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.17,0:36:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹营处处都是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.61,0:36:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹操事事都诡计多端
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.97,0:36:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}由此可见
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.74,0:36:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}世人已经被那个曹操给吓怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.51,0:36:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实那个曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.35,0:36:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}远没有那么强大
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.69,0:36:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可正是在你们这些人心目中
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.12,0:36:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对他的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.46,0:36:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}助长那个曹操的强大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.03,0:36:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸 你放肆了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.56,0:36:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.10,0:36:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公恕罪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.97,0:36:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 在下偶尔放肆一下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.01,0:36:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要远比那曹孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.91,0:37:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放肆一生要强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.32,0:37:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 田丰已在狱中伏剑
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.83,0:37:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.13,0:37:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}死了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.17,0:37:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}田丰可有遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.54,0:37:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}田别驾临死前
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.04,0:37:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为主公留下一封书信
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.22,0:37:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我心乱如麻 还是你念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.06,0:37:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.53,0:37:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当在下的死讯到主公的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.10,0:37:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公一定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.57,0:37:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为在下虽然恃才傲上
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.31,0:37:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但在下罪不至死
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.31,0:38:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主令在下死
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.84,0:38:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定有小人进谗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.95,0:38:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个小人就是貌似忠诚的许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.69,0:38:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸跟曹操是少年密友
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.09,0:38:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}同窗发小
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.06,0:38:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们藕断丝连 鸿雁传书
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.03,0:38:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果主公胜了曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.00,0:38:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸会竭诚尽忠主公
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.90,0:38:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果主公败于曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.00,0:38:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸会背主投敌
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.11,0:38:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.42,0:38:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.38,0:38:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个田丰在临死之前
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.62,0:38:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还要在我的心窝子上
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.02,0:38:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}捅上一刀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.63,0:38:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.93,0:38:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是否与那曹操是发小
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.00,0:38:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 禀主公
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.90,0:39:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸的老家和那曹操的老家
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.87,0:39:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相距不过二里
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.64,0:39:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}少时
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.61,0:39:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也曾与那曹操同窗共读
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.88,0:39:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.48,0:39:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自从我许攸决意跟随主公以来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.78,0:39:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就与那曹贼
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.55,0:39:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生不两立 死不相容
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.79,0:39:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有没有和曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.36,0:39:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}互通鸿雁 藕断丝连
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.13,0:39:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有 没有 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.09,0:39:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 万万没有
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.76,0:39:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这一定是那田丰对我的诬陷哪
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.27,0:39:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 这常言道
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.64,0:39:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人之将死 其言也哀
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.54,0:39:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那这田丰在临死之前
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.51,0:39:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对我的诬陷
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.24,0:39:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定是格外动人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.11,0:39:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.68,0:39:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸 你屡进谗言 害死田丰
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.82,0:39:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这个头先暂时寄存在你这
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.92,0:39:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等我灭了曹贼
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.86,0:39:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我再明察严办
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.23,0:40:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}退下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.05,0:40:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}庸主 庸主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.19,0:40:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忠言逆耳
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.59,0:40:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}庸主不足于谋
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.56,0:40:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如此下去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.49,0:40:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我早晚要步田丰之后尘
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.36,0:41:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.52,0:41:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 外面有一位来客
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.39,0:41:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自称是主公旧友许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.23,0:41:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请求拜见主公
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.73,0:41:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸
